{"tid":718180,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"請問這間scan菲林ok唔okay?","createTime":"2018-06-26T15:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T04:30:56.000Z","uid":185507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"753e7caac102bcb297cafcab0562ae525502842f","tid":718180,"uid":185507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/225724_9d4747a5997320d008066fc845a587ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F225724_9d4747a5997320d008066fc845a587ee.jpg&h=b86473ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/225730_ed112416434247b846c18109adcd37e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F225730_ed112416434247b846c18109adcd37e4.jpg&h=f436d19d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一幅是原圖, 第二幅是右上角<br />\n菲林是用Velvia 50, M645, 是朋友介紹 用Drum scanner scan, 有效像素5000萬 收$250. 請問各位師兄這個質素可以嗎?"},{"pid":"06bd625bd31c32eb132304505fd14c80f002b787","tid":718180,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:04:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71f3c3f382c00edc1ca088db126fdb3c4ec95916","tid":718180,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"753e7caac102bcb297cafcab0562ae525502842f","tid":718180,"uid":185507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/225724_9d4747a5997320d008066fc845a587ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F225724_9d4747a5997320d008066fc845a587ee.jpg&h=b86473ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/225730_ed112416434247b846c18109adcd37e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F225730_ed112416434247b846c18109adcd37e4.jpg&h=f436d19d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一幅是原圖, 第二幅是右上角<br />\n菲林是用Velvia 50, M645, 是朋友介紹 用Drum scanner scan, 有效像素5000萬 收$250. 請問各位師兄這個質素可以嗎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"scan 得幾好 wor。<br />\n<br />\n係邊間呀？ For The Art？<br />\n<br />\n未試過 用 Drum Scan，因為影得麻麻，唔想浪費錢。"},{"pid":"fc1b84d6a28f9660e54f82d830ee3606efbef40c","tid":718180,"uid":11779,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"本來我覺得好一般，但一睇你放大果幅，屌，原來仲可以再放大。<br />\n<br />\n介紹間野比為師啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473f80e441518b598156254a90d7388b2ee457e9","tid":718180,"uid":150807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T01:03:36.000Z","msg":"點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0443a8862afb3f11b80678274b8e04dc7f04ea53","tid":718180,"uid":11779,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/125814_7a3c5497355c5fa4ac8a6ce7e05144a3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F125814_7a3c5497355c5fa4ac8a6ce7e05144a3.jpeg&h=b9ef949c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘩屌，呀叔我影左咁多年菲林都唔知可以放到咁大，同部phase one 有得比。<br />\n介紹比人啦，攝影界收皮就係因為太多好似啲你咁嘅仆街將啲好野收收埋埋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9570876dfafb481f566474abe083ad2f3516cf02","tid":718180,"uid":18388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"唔差"},{"pid":"8246fd026f2c9cb1a81440a4f9c81422b33e9d81","tid":718180,"uid":135896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"原圖都係5千萬像素，iso 100+腳架, 舊菲林scanner minolta 5400<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1829/43082239541_b696163345_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1829%2F43082239541_b696163345_o.jpg&h=7d5533af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1785/42177506435_a1bd834831_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1785%2F42177506435_a1bd834831_o.jpg&h=2289b06d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDrumscan係好，不過好睇你本身scan嗰張菲林解像度夠唔夠，iso100, set晒腳架，其實普通2000零萬像素已經夠，你再勁既scanner, 如果原圖唔夠像素，其實等於倒錢落海"},{"pid":"adeb3080f118efda5867722d9d220eec374fadaa","tid":718180,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"120 size 呢個質素勉強啦<br />\n講到好似好撚勁咁又想呃新手啊？<br />\n你邊間黑店架？"},{"pid":"1fc00d3e53a630d8c42c3db6c5f928cb4bc04814","tid":718180,"uid":167735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>120 size 呢個質素勉強啦<br />\n講到好似好撚勁咁又想呃新手啊？<br />\n你邊間黑店架？</blockquote><br />\n$250 scan 應該無新手岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92b7f946c50ebfd1e1490c9402b327e3aadbfe6","tid":718180,"uid":18111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"有興趣，分享 okay?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee662378ecbffc1f7c56441f00795a9012406d4","tid":718180,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fc00d3e53a630d8c42c3db6c5f928cb4bc04814","tid":718180,"uid":167735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>120 size 呢個質素勉強啦<br />\n講到好似好撚勁咁又想呃新手啊？<br />\n你邊間黑店架？</blockquote><br />\n$250 scan 應該無新手岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T12:15:33.000Z","msg":"Per frame定per roll？"},{"pid":"0c6a0bff480c1b3ac7d9c2781e28caa3997e9a6a","tid":718180,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adeb3080f118efda5867722d9d220eec374f